    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "sendMessage",
        "chatId": "={{ $('Extract Command').first().json.chatId }}",
        "text": "=\ud83e\udd16 *AI Agent Bot - Tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap*\n\n\ud83d\udcdd *T\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung:*\n/generate <ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1> - T\u1ea1o b\u00e0i LinkedIn\n/suggest - AI g\u1ee3i \u00fd 5 topic ideas\n/addtopic <topic>|<pillar>|<priority> - Th\u00eam topic\n\n\ud83d\udccb *Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd n\u1ed9i dung:*\n/status - Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea content queue\n/pending - B\u00e0i ch\u1edd review\n/view <id> - Xem n\u1ed9i dung \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7\n/approve <id> - Duy\u1ec7t b\u00e0i\n/reject <id> <l\u00fd do> - T\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0i\n\n\ud83d\udccc *Topics:*\n/topics - Xem topics ch\u01b0a d\u00f9ng\n\n\ud83d\ude80 *\u0110\u0103ng b\u00e0i:*\n/post\\_linkedin - L\u1ea5y b\u00e0i LI approved \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng\n/post\\_fb - L\u1ea5y b\u00e0i FB approved\n/published <id> <url> - C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng\n\n\ud83d\udd27 *H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng:*\n/health - Ki\u1ec3m tra services\n/help - Hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap",
        "additionalFields": {"parse_mode": "Markdown"}
      },
